snippet.title: BigCliveLive
snippet.description:
A second channel for live streams and face videos, to protect the innocent from the harsh reality that my face does not match my voice.  It will also be the home of the MBC - Manx Beard Club videos (just a group of beardy friends).

A British TV licence is NOT required to view my videos or almost every other video on YouTube.

Try to think of this as a "personal" channel with personal opinions, but not getting too involved with politics or other divisive material.

There may be occasional drinking of adult beverages, and there may be mild profanities - but only in a jovial manner as is common in Britain.

The best way to view this channel is to grab a drink and some snacks and join me at the table.

The main channel is at bigclivedotcom  https://www.youtube.com/bigclivedotcom
